    • Constructor Detail

      • ImageButton

        public ImageButton(java.lang.String onImageURL,
                   java.lang.String offImageURL,
                   DisplayCommand command,
                   java.lang.String offTipText,
                   java.lang.String onTipText)
        Create an image that launches an action when clicked once. Normally, a toggle with two states. Styled so that images and toolTips are swapped when the state swaps
        Parameters:
        onImageURL - the image to show in the 'on' state
        offImageURL - the image to show in the 'off' state
        command - the {link capitalism.view.command} to execute
        offTipText - the tooltip to display in the off state
        onTipText - the tooltip to display in the on state
